Config files.
--------------------------------
init.vim  -> ~/.config/nvim/init.vim       | Neovim config.
gtk.css   -> ~/.config/gtk-3.0/gtk.css     | For terminal padding.
xmonad.hs -> ~/.xmonad/xmonad.hs           | Window manager config.
termite.config -> ~/.config/termite/config | Terminal font and color settings.


Good to have Projects
--------------------------------
https://github.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts    | Symbols and patched fonts.
https://github.com/powerline/fonts         | Powerline patched fonts.
https://github.com/Corwind/termite-install | Installation script for terminal.
